   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To the sitologoi of the village of Karanis, greeting. I, Ammon, son of Harpokras(?), of the public (cultivators) of the 86th cleruchy of Karanis, have received from you as loan of seed grain for the present 23rd year from the grain of the past 22nd year, 3 1/2 artabai of wheat. I, Chairemon, son of Pamounis, have written for him because he is illiterate. (2nd hand) I, Kastor, agoranomos, have signed for three and one-half artabai. Year 23, Hadrianos 30.</ab>
         </div>
